labels.searchTipsA1: The search engine uses the keywords to match products that contain ALL keywords. For example: a search for "ibm desktop p4" will match products that contain ibm, desktop, AND p4. This is different than some search engines which will find products that match ibm OR desktop OR p4 exclusively.
labels.searchTipsA2: Type in the part number and click the "GO" button. Note: If the part number contains dashes, slashes, or other punctuation, you can omit the punctuation and quick search will still find the product.
